APPENDIX B: Daily Checklist for Server Administrator
Morning:
☐ Verify SQL Server service is running
☐ Check disk space (maintain >20% free)
☐ Review backup logs for last night's backup

Weekly:
☐ Verify all client computers can connect
☐ Check backup file sizes are reasonable
☐ Review error logs in Event Viewer

Monthly:
☐ Run database maintenance script
☐ Test restore from backup
☐ Update Windows and SQL Server patches
☐ Review and clean old backup files
